1
00:00:06,112 --> 00:00:10,144
(2000, a week before
Nie Feng went abroad)

2
00:00:20,244 --> 00:00:21,244
Governor Nie,

3
00:00:21,564 --> 00:00:22,244
finished?

4
00:00:23,404 --> 00:00:24,645
Your Highness,

5
00:00:24,645 --> 00:00:25,645
please help me this once.

6
00:00:34,045 --> 00:00:35,365
Look up.

7
00:01:04,444 --> 00:01:05,844
Time flies so fast.

8
00:01:07,045 --> 00:01:08,565
You even have white hairs now.

9
00:01:10,364 --> 00:01:11,564
Then look at me.

10
00:01:12,204 --> 00:01:13,525
Have I aged too?

11
00:01:14,805 --> 00:01:16,004
You haven't changed,

12
00:01:17,004 --> 00:01:18,924
just like when we first met,

13
00:01:19,488 --> 00:01:20,564
radiant.

14
00:01:22,165 --> 00:01:23,965
Why don't you look at me?

15
00:01:31,805 --> 00:01:32,965
Liar.

16
00:01:33,844 --> 00:01:35,924
You men are all liars,

17
00:01:36,320 --> 00:01:37,685
especially you,

18
00:01:37,685 --> 00:01:38,764
Nie Changlong.

19
00:01:39,445 --> 00:01:40,885
You ungrateful,

20
00:01:40,885 --> 00:01:42,245
heartless scoundrel!

21
00:01:43,605 --> 00:01:45,165
Now you come begging me?

22
00:01:46,124 --> 00:01:48,004
Where were you back then?

23
00:01:52,764 --> 00:01:53,564
Leave.

24
00:01:54,204 --> 00:01:55,644
Whether you survive this hurdle

25
00:01:55,965 --> 00:01:57,685
depends entirely on your own fate.

26
00:02:09,644 --> 00:02:10,245
Feng,

27
00:02:10,400 --> 00:02:11,404
close the curtains.

28
00:02:16,005 --> 00:02:16,605
Dad,

29
00:02:17,405 --> 00:02:18,524
what's going on?

30
00:02:22,804 --> 00:02:23,524
Feng,

31
00:02:24,845 --> 00:02:26,084
early morning in three days,

32
00:02:26,084 --> 00:02:26,964
fly to Vancouver.

33
00:02:28,005 --> 00:02:29,605
Someone will meet you at the airport.

34
00:02:30,165 --> 00:02:32,005
Your bank card and passport are here.

35
00:02:32,644 --> 00:02:34,964
I also have some overseas accounts.

36
00:02:35,964 --> 00:02:37,364
The person meeting you

37
00:02:37,364 --> 00:02:39,104
will give you all the details.

38
00:02:40,045 --> 00:02:41,165
What happened?

39
00:02:41,565 --> 00:02:42,845
You killed the Yanyue Gang's

40
00:02:43,005 --> 00:02:44,644
Huang Weide personally?

41
00:02:45,885 --> 00:02:46,684
No.

42
00:02:47,285 --> 00:02:48,484
I used Jiasheng to do it.

43
00:02:48,725 --> 00:02:49,445
What's wrong?

44
00:02:50,445 --> 00:02:51,445
Don't you realize

45
00:02:51,445 --> 00:02:53,445
that isn't his real target?

46
00:02:54,125 --> 00:02:56,224
I don't know how the ledger got to him,

47
00:02:56,924 --> 00:02:57,605
but

48
00:02:58,204 --> 00:02:59,360
he came to Luosen

49
00:02:59,360 --> 00:03:00,864
to specifically aim at our family.

50
00:03:01,684 --> 00:03:02,605
You mean

51
00:03:03,644 --> 00:03:05,725
Huang Weide also had a ledger?

52
00:03:07,084 --> 00:03:08,285
Now that he's dead,

53
00:03:08,684 --> 00:03:09,845
the ledger

54
00:03:12,405 --> 00:03:14,285
is in Tu Jiasheng's hands.

55
00:03:15,285 --> 00:03:16,084
Of course!

56
00:03:16,445 --> 00:03:18,045
Otherwise, how could it have vanished?

57
00:03:20,605 --> 00:03:21,405
I understand.

58
00:03:22,524 --> 00:03:23,804
I'll go to Jiasheng right now.

59
00:03:24,605 --> 00:03:25,764
We're sworn brothers.

60
00:03:26,885 --> 00:03:27,924
He won't refuse me.

61
00:03:28,364 --> 00:03:28,924
Feng,

62
00:03:29,845 --> 00:03:30,720
anyway,

63
00:03:30,720 --> 00:03:32,764
early morning in three days,
you must leave.

64
00:03:33,005 --> 00:03:35,605
(Anti-Corruption Team Intervenes)
The Cabinet's onto me now.

65
00:03:36,165 --> 00:03:37,845
I likely won't survive this.

66
00:03:37,920 --> 00:03:38,684
But

67
00:03:38,924 --> 00:03:40,684
I must ensure your future is secure.

68
00:03:40,684 --> 00:03:41,244
Dad,

69
00:03:42,405 --> 00:03:44,125
go to the Grand Princess.

70
00:03:44,605 --> 00:03:46,445
She will help you.

71
00:03:50,560 --> 00:03:51,524
It won't help.

72
00:03:55,084 --> 00:03:58,016
She still resents me
for what happened back then.

73
00:04:06,165 --> 00:04:06,725
Dad,

74
00:04:08,565 --> 00:04:09,964
I'll go to Jiasheng now.

75
00:04:11,204 --> 00:04:13,125
He has influence
with the Grand Princess.

76
00:04:14,924 --> 00:04:16,804
I won't leave you alone to face this.

77
00:04:25,376 --> 00:04:27,040
(Cabinet Anti-Corruption
Investigation Team Intervenes)

78
00:04:27,040 --> 00:04:30,304
=The Glory Fades=

79
00:04:30,304 --> 00:04:32,992
=Episode 31=
(Choices)

80
00:04:44,924 --> 00:04:45,564
Where's Feng?

81
00:04:53,405 --> 00:04:54,324
What is it?

82
00:04:55,484 --> 00:04:57,004
So you get nervous too.

83
00:05:03,484 --> 00:05:04,684
Since you're not dead,

84
00:05:04,992 --> 00:05:06,085
our score

85
00:05:06,405 --> 00:05:07,525
isn't settled.

86
00:05:09,564 --> 00:05:12,364
You'd better settle
your score with Feng first.

87
00:05:51,648 --> 00:05:52,960
(Account login)

88
00:05:56,896 --> 00:05:58,560
(File encrypted. Enter fingerprint
to unlock and continue access.)

89
00:06:12,064 --> 00:06:13,856
(Unlocked)

90
00:06:25,408 --> 00:06:26,368
(No content in this folder)

91
00:06:31,552 --> 00:06:33,216
(No content in this folder)

92
00:06:49,924 --> 00:06:50,484
Hello.

93
00:06:51,444 --> 00:06:52,205
I'm in.

94
00:06:52,765 --> 00:06:54,205
But the folders are empty.

95
00:06:54,525 --> 00:06:55,725
They must have been moved.

96
00:06:56,045 --> 00:06:56,684
Okay.

97
00:06:57,364 --> 00:06:58,244
Got it.

98
00:07:02,405 --> 00:07:03,324
Don't stop!

99
00:07:03,725 --> 00:07:04,725
Keep singing!

100
00:07:30,924 --> 00:07:31,725
Hello,

101
00:07:32,045 --> 00:07:32,845
Jiasheng.

102
00:07:36,324 --> 00:07:37,244
Long time no see,

103
00:07:37,645 --> 00:07:38,285
Feng.

104
00:07:43,924 --> 00:07:44,884
You forget again.

105
00:07:45,765 --> 00:07:46,884
What should you call me?

106
00:07:49,085 --> 00:07:49,765
I didn't forget.

107
00:07:51,085 --> 00:07:51,965
But as you

108
00:07:52,525 --> 00:07:53,725
called me here,

109
00:07:54,205 --> 00:07:56,165
we should catch up first.

110
00:08:00,205 --> 00:08:01,205
Right,

111
00:08:01,525 --> 00:08:02,285
catch up.

112
00:08:02,684 --> 00:08:04,324
Catch up first.

113
00:08:04,804 --> 00:08:05,884
Come, Jiasheng.

114
00:08:06,124 --> 00:08:07,525
Let me give you a proper hug.

115
00:08:14,324 --> 00:08:15,605
Look at you.

116
00:08:16,484 --> 00:08:18,004
Haven't seen you in so many years,

117
00:08:18,605 --> 00:08:20,605
yet you've kept such a fine figure.

118
00:08:21,364 --> 00:08:23,884
No wonder
women can't help but adore you.

119
00:08:26,045 --> 00:08:26,484
Come,

120
00:08:26,884 --> 00:08:27,684
sit inside.

121
00:08:27,804 --> 00:08:28,924
Sit and chat.

122
00:08:28,924 --> 00:08:30,004
Come on.

123
00:08:31,205 --> 00:08:31,804
Feng,

124
00:08:33,124 --> 00:08:33,605
after you.

125
00:08:46,604 --> 00:08:47,604
Feng.

126
00:08:50,005 --> 00:08:50,804
Ruxue,

127
00:08:51,285 --> 00:08:52,844
where are your manners?

128
00:08:53,564 --> 00:08:55,045
Aren't you going to greet

129
00:08:55,485 --> 00:08:56,684
your boss properly?

130
00:09:01,684 --> 00:09:02,485
Hello, Mr. Tu.

131
00:09:03,885 --> 00:09:05,844
Feng specially prepared for you

132
00:09:05,844 --> 00:09:06,765
all kinds of beverages.

133
00:09:06,964 --> 00:09:07,645
Which one

134
00:09:07,844 --> 00:09:08,960
would you like?

135
00:09:12,204 --> 00:09:13,804
Look, Ruxue

136
00:09:14,204 --> 00:09:15,604
is still so thoughtful.

137
00:09:16,804 --> 00:09:17,724
Jiasheng,

138
00:09:18,365 --> 00:09:20,125
sometimes I muse,

139
00:09:20,405 --> 00:09:21,885
that she's been by your side

140
00:09:21,885 --> 00:09:23,604
for so many years,

141
00:09:24,204 --> 00:09:26,365
yet she still holds
such lingering affection

142
00:09:26,365 --> 00:09:27,765
for me, her former boss.

143
00:09:29,285 --> 00:09:31,525
If everyone in this world

144
00:09:31,525 --> 00:09:33,525
were as loyal as she is,

145
00:09:34,285 --> 00:09:35,525
how wonderful that would be.

146
00:09:58,885 --> 00:10:00,084
When did you join Feng?

147
00:10:03,405 --> 00:10:04,005
Mr. Zhao,

148
00:10:04,444 --> 00:10:05,804
I've never joined anyone.

149
00:10:15,365 --> 00:10:16,204
For Su Yunian?

150
00:10:16,765 --> 00:10:17,604
You like her?

151
00:10:18,204 --> 00:10:19,405
She joined Jiasheng,

152
00:10:19,765 --> 00:10:20,405
right?

153
00:10:27,005 --> 00:10:28,645
If I'm not mistaken,

154
00:10:29,564 --> 00:10:31,204
Su Yunian isn't actually with Feng.

155
00:10:31,204 --> 00:10:32,285
It's just a recording.

156
00:10:32,804 --> 00:10:33,885
Am I guessing correctly?

157
00:10:35,964 --> 00:10:37,285
I knew I couldn't fool you.

158
00:10:39,285 --> 00:10:40,804
She gave you the fingerprint.

159
00:10:46,724 --> 00:10:48,405
Poor Jiasheng.

160
00:10:49,005 --> 00:10:50,684
Before he left, he specifically told me

161
00:10:50,684 --> 00:10:52,365
to take good care of Su Yunian.

162
00:11:16,416 --> 00:11:18,365
He only protected her like a sister.

163
00:11:18,765 --> 00:11:19,285
Got it?

164
00:11:19,964 --> 00:11:20,645
Take this.

165
00:11:21,408 --> 00:11:23,200
No one at Deep In The Bustle
will stop you.

166
00:11:23,365 --> 00:11:25,125
This is the most I can help you.

167
00:11:28,204 --> 00:11:29,005
Thank you, Lu.

168
00:11:39,204 --> 00:11:39,964
Jiasheng,

169
00:11:40,604 --> 00:11:42,485
from the day you first joined me,

170
00:11:42,485 --> 00:11:43,365
I knew

171
00:11:43,964 --> 00:11:45,405
you were different from Qin Wei.

172
00:11:46,765 --> 00:11:49,165
You were single-mindedly determined
to climb up.

173
00:11:49,765 --> 00:11:50,804
To climb up,

174
00:11:50,804 --> 00:11:52,604
you'd use any means necessary.

175
00:11:53,405 --> 00:11:54,084
No problem.

176
00:11:54,604 --> 00:11:55,964
That's fine.

177
00:11:56,285 --> 00:11:57,804
We all get what we need, right?

178
00:11:58,485 --> 00:12:00,485
As long as you want to climb up,

179
00:12:00,604 --> 00:12:03,684
I can pull you up by hand.

180
00:12:04,724 --> 00:12:05,885
But you must understand.

181
00:12:06,405 --> 00:12:07,964
Starting an enterprise is easy,

182
00:12:07,964 --> 00:12:09,645
but keeping it is hard.

183
00:12:11,804 --> 00:12:14,964
Especially for rootless leaves,

184
00:12:15,765 --> 00:12:17,165
one wrong step,

185
00:12:17,724 --> 00:12:18,964
and it becomes

186
00:12:19,165 --> 00:12:21,885
an unwarranted disaster,
like flowers in a mirror,

187
00:12:22,645 --> 00:12:24,964
or the moon in water.

188
00:12:28,285 --> 00:12:29,005
Jiasheng,

189
00:12:29,485 --> 00:12:30,684
why are you standing?

190
00:12:30,964 --> 00:12:31,525
Sit.

191
00:12:32,804 --> 00:12:34,005
Come.

192
00:12:34,005 --> 00:12:35,684
Take a seat.

193
00:12:38,204 --> 00:12:38,885
Here.

194
00:12:39,324 --> 00:12:40,005
Look,

195
00:12:41,324 --> 00:12:43,365
how much I think of you.

196
00:12:45,684 --> 00:12:47,604
Once, like me and Lu,

197
00:12:48,204 --> 00:12:50,724
you loved this old-fashioned soda best.

198
00:12:51,964 --> 00:12:53,324
But one day,

199
00:12:53,525 --> 00:12:56,084
after tasting the artisanal coffee,

200
00:12:56,084 --> 00:12:59,165
you developed a special fondness for it.

201
00:13:00,485 --> 00:13:02,005
Now I hear

202
00:13:02,005 --> 00:13:03,645
you exclusively favor

203
00:13:03,645 --> 00:13:06,365
the estate peat-smoke whiskey.

204
00:13:07,804 --> 00:13:09,964
Today, I prepared all three for you.

205
00:13:11,765 --> 00:13:12,405
Jiasheng,

206
00:13:13,684 --> 00:13:14,804
make a choice.

207
00:13:26,365 --> 00:13:27,045
Feng,

208
00:13:28,964 --> 00:13:30,324
adults don't make choices.

209
00:13:30,724 --> 00:13:31,405
I want all.

210
00:13:38,924 --> 00:13:41,084
Oh Tu Jiasheng,

211
00:13:41,964 --> 00:13:43,405
seems An Ruoxi

212
00:13:43,405 --> 00:13:45,924
didn't die a worthy death at all!

213
00:13:46,405 --> 00:13:49,604
It taught you absolutely no lesson.

214
00:13:51,684 --> 00:13:53,804
But I wonder if adding

215
00:13:53,804 --> 00:13:54,964
Su Yunian,

216
00:13:54,964 --> 00:13:55,964
would it

217
00:13:56,084 --> 00:13:57,285
double the effect?

218
00:14:04,084 --> 00:14:04,724
Feng,

219
00:14:05,844 --> 00:14:06,604
let her go!

220
00:14:07,724 --> 00:14:08,765
It's not her fault.

221
00:14:09,365 --> 00:14:10,204
As for other things,

222
00:14:11,005 --> 00:14:12,365
we can talk.

223
00:14:13,405 --> 00:14:14,405
Jiasheng,

224
00:14:15,324 --> 00:14:16,924
do you think you're

225
00:14:17,684 --> 00:14:19,885
still qualified to negotiate with me?

226
00:14:20,165 --> 00:14:20,844
Yes,

227
00:14:21,804 --> 00:14:22,844
not qualified.

228
00:14:24,005 --> 00:14:24,844
Feng,

229
00:14:26,165 --> 00:14:27,485
I just want to ask you one thing.

230
00:14:29,280 --> 00:14:30,365
Did you

231
00:14:30,765 --> 00:14:32,365
send someone to kill An Ruoxi?

232
00:14:40,116 --> 00:14:43,790
♪If the heart can't hear the sorrow♪

233
00:14:44,089 --> 00:14:47,280
♪It only makes everything look so fake♪

234
00:14:49,112 --> 00:14:52,733
♪Your eyes resemble hers too much♪

235
00:14:53,282 --> 00:14:56,081
♪Who makes me forget whom♪

236
00:14:57,552 --> 00:15:01,282
♪The warmth in my heart is fading♪

237
00:15:01,506 --> 00:15:05,003
♪Every glance feels like atonement♪

238
00:15:06,402 --> 00:15:10,089
♪Ambiguity hidden in the night breeze♪

239
00:15:10,727 --> 00:15:15,842
♪Blows away the chance to explain♪

240
00:15:16,546 --> 00:15:20,680
♪I feel guilty♪

241
00:15:21,250 --> 00:15:24,994
♪I'll have no regrets
even I leave quietly♪

242
00:15:25,858 --> 00:15:29,301
♪Even in tears♪

243
00:15:30,050 --> 00:15:33,964
♪It doesn't matter♪

244
00:15:34,146 --> 00:15:37,969
♪We embrace in dreams♪

245
00:15:38,818 --> 00:15:42,256
♪I let down all my defenses♪

246
00:15:43,490 --> 00:15:46,853
♪Though the story has its end♪

247
00:15:47,618 --> 00:15:55,970
♪I'll journey with you all my life♪
